<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.10.8">
<l>muṭiyuṭai yamarark kiṭarceyyu macurar tamperu māṉaiyaṉ ṟariyāy</l>
<l>maṭiyiṭai vaittu mārpaimuṉ kīṇṭa māyaṉār maṉṉiya kōyil</l>
<l>paṭiyiṭai māṭat taṭiyiṭait tūṇil patittapaṉ maṇikaḷi ṉoḷiyāl</l>
<l>viṭipaka liraveṉ ṟaṟivari tāya tiruveḷḷi yaṅkuṭi yatuvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple where dwells the dark one who, as a lion</l>
<l rend="indent">having placed on his thigh the great lord of the demons</l>
<l>Who made trouble for the crowned immortals, split [his] chest in front,</l>
<l>Is that very one - Tiruveḷḷiyaṅkuṭi where it becomes difficult</l>
<l rend="indent">knowing dawn, day, or night,</l>
<l>Due to the glare from a myriad of jewels inlaid on columns,</l>
<l rend="indent">along bases of mansions and along porticos.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
